Author: bluebrainbethany
Text: Thank you ♥️ I feel like I threw my car in reverse and backed the fuck off a cliff. I ended up not purging my last binge. If my body wanted food that badly then I guess it prolly needed it.. just really nervous about tomorrow. My weigh in will be higher and I’ll feel bloated at the gym which might lead to a crappy workout which might lead to another binge :( I have a ball of stress in my stomach :(

Author: chuckthehills
Text: Speed bumps happen, try not to beat yourself up too much for it! Tomorrow will be a new day. Wow my comment is very cliche but I mean it lol <3
